input.activity_signal: Recent FCC filing for VoIP Numbering Authorization on 2023-11-17, which indicates active regulatory compliance. Company founded in 2014 with established email domain (elevitt@1pcom.com) and key personnel including CEO Erik Levitt and COO Kristen Vasicek.
